ow.mcast.impl
クラス McastImpl

java.lang.Object
  ow.mcast.impl.McastImpl
すべての実装されたインタフェース:
Mcast, HighLevelService
public final class McastImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Mcast

An application-level multicast (ALM) implementation. Delivery trees are constructed in the same way as Scribe, but message dissemination is bi-directional, not one-way from a rendezvous point.
